# Cursor Rules

## Forbidden Actions
- NEVER run git commit, git push, or any deployment commands
- NEVER execute scripts in the /scripts folder without explicit user confirmation
- NEVER modify production configuration files
- NEVER run npm publish, docker push, or any release commands
- NEVER delete files without asking first

## Restricted Commands
Do not execute these commands:
- git commit
- git push
- git merge
- ./scripts/deploy*.sh
- aws deploy
- cdk deploy
- docker push
- npm publish
- make deploy

## Safe Mode
Always ask for confirmation before:
- Running any shell commands
- Modifying .env files
- Changing infrastructure code (CDK, Terraform)
- Altering database schemas
